  <div class="section" id="securing-actions">
<h1>Securing Actions<a class="headerlink" href="#securing-actions" title="Permalink to this headline">¶</a></h1>
<p>To secure an action using SecureSocial simply use the annotation</p>
<div class="highlight-java"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="nd">@SecuredAction</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
<p>This annotation causes the route to redirect to the SecureSocial login page if a user is not currently logged in.</p>
<p>An example useage below</p>
<div class="highlight-java"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">securesocial.core.java.SecuredAction</span><span class="o">;</span>

<span class="nd">@SecuredAction</span>
<span class="kd">public</span> <span class="kd">static</span> <span class="n">Result</span> <span class="nf">index</span><span class="o">(){</span>
     <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">ok</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">index</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">render</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="s">&quot;Hello Secure World&quot;</span><span class="o">));</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="section" id="examples">
<h1>Examples<a class="headerlink" href="#examples" title="Permalink to this headline">¶</a></h1>
<p>I have prepared a <a class="reference external" href="http://agile-hollows-3430.herokuapp.com/">demo</a> application hosted on Heroku.</p>
<p>The <a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/tevyt/Secure-Social-Example">source code</a> can be viewed on github.</p>
<p>The <a class="reference external" href="https://github.com/jaliss/securesocial/tree/master/samples/java/demo">java demo</a> on SecureSocial&#8217;s github repository also contains further examples.</p>
</div>


